      <title>韩国监管机构审查摩根士丹利的 SK 海力士卖单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/morgan-stanley-s-hynix-sell-order-faces-fss-review-yonhap-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国金融监管机构正在调查摩根士丹利要求其出售 SK 海力士股票的决定，此前该行研究分析师下调了对该股的评级，这是韩国对全球银行和对冲基金加强审查的又一迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/morgan-stanley-s-hynix-sell-order-faces-fss-review-yonhap-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 04:22:48 GMT</pubDate>
